00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:15.000
Coach Jessica:  You're very welcome.  Now, shifting gears a bit, I know we've talked a lot about planning and implementing differentiation, but it's also important to reflect on the process.

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:30.000
Emily:  That's true.  I sometimes forget to take the time to reflect on how things went and what I can learn from my experiences.

00:16:31.000 --> 00:16:45.000
Coach Jessica:  Reflection is a crucial part of growth and improvement.  It allows you to identify your successes and challenges, and to make adjustments for the future.

